# ── OS noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo

# ── Editors / IDEs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace
.history/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj

# ── Claude Code local state ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Per-user settings + session memory; should never enter the shared repo.
.claude/

# ── Environment files ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Per-developer overrides: ignored everywhere. `.env` itself is NOT
# globbed — frontend apps under Vite ship a tracked `.env` with
# build-time constants (VITE_APP_TITLE etc.). Anchor secret-style
# .env files to the repo root only.
/.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
# Anchored to the repo root — bare `logs/` would match any directory
# named logs at any depth, including the frontend view at
# frontend/apps/admin/src/views/kumo/logs/.
/logs/
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# ── Go (backend/) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Build outputs from `go build`. The Docker pipeline builds inside the
# image; local `make host-build` writes into deploy/out/ (covered below).
backend/admin-service
backend/iris
backend/seed
backend/loadgen
backend/bin/

# Stray binaries from `go build ./...` runs that drop ELF outputs into
# their source dir. Each cmd/ entrypoint that someone might `go build`
# in-place gets ignored here.
backend/scripts/loadgen/loadgen
backend/app/admin/service/cmd/server/server
backend/app/admin/service/cmd/seed/seed

*.test
*.out
*.prof
coverage.html
coverage.txt

# Go workspace files (used by IDEs; per-developer)
go.work
go.work.sum

# ── Frontend (frontend/) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# frontend/ has its own .gitignore (node_modules, dist, .turbo, …).
# Keep this top-level file from shadowing it.

# ── Deploy / build artefacts ────────────────────────────────────────
# `make host-build` and `make host-package` write here:
#   deploy/out/iris               static binary
#   deploy/out/iris-host.tar.gz   shippable tarball
deploy/out/

# ── kumomta runtime data ────────────────────────────────────────────
# DKIM PRIVATE KEYS must never enter git. The directory is bind-mounted
# into the kumomta container; we keep the dir present via .gitkeep.
kumomta/etc/dkim/*.pem
kumomta/etc/dkim/*.key

# Generated logs and spool from the kumomta container, when bind-mounted
# locally for debugging.
kumomta/logs/
kumomta/spool/

# ── Embedded SPA (managed by its own .gitignore) ────────────────────
# backend/pkg/spa/dist/ has a per-dir .gitignore that excludes the
# pnpm build output but keeps PLACEHOLDER + .gitignore tracked. Don't
# duplicate the rule here — it would shadow the per-dir one.
